Web Vulnerabilities are common entry for attackers, in this post we'll explore **Sql-Injection** and **XSS**--two of the OWASP top 10.

## SQL-Injection
This Occurs when Unsanitized input is used in database query.

## XSS
Cross-site Scripting allows attackers to inject.

